        "title": "feat(windows): add taskbar tray companion",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Add a native Windows taskbar tray companion under `Windows/` with repository status rows, local git state, recent GitHub lists, traffic/heatmap/changelog summaries, Actions queue/billing/runner details, rate-limit diagnostics, PR notifications, issue navigator, preferences, named account profiles, GitHub App OAuth, account-scoped Credential Manager token storage, ETag cache, archive-backed issue/PR fallback, launch-at-login, update checks, and installer packaging.\n- Add Windows build/package/smoke/Crabbox scripts, including smoke JSON artifacts and best-effort desktop screenshot capture, plus a Windows CI job.\n- Document Windows setup and the remaining parity roadmap.\n\n## Validation\n- `CRABBOX_PROVIDER=aws CRABBOX_TARGET=windows pnpm windows:crabbox`\n- Crabbox run `run_c0fbb13478cb`: Windows Server 10.0.20348, .NET SDK 8.0.421, `dotnet build` succeeded with 0 warnings/errors, `dotnet test` passed 52 tests, `smoke_windows.ps1` published and launched `RepoBar.Windows.exe`, verified the generated settings file, and wrote a smoke JSON summary. Desktop screenshot capture was attempted but reported unavailable in the SSH runner (`CopyFromScreen`: invalid handle).\n- Earlier Crabbox run `run_db7b36899b00`: validated the archive-backed issue/PR fallback with 52 passing tests and smoke launch/settings verification.\n- Earlier Crabbox run `run_c168edc023e0`: validated GitHub App OAuth + named account profile work with 50 passing tests and smoke launch/settings verification.\n\n## Notes\n- This is a draft because Windows is now end-to-end build/test/smoke validated for the implemented tray surface, OAuth, account profiles, and archive-backed issue/PR fallback, but not true full macOS feature parity yet. The main remaining gap is captured notification-area UI proof from an interactive desktop session.\n- The current hosted SSH proof validates process launch/settings generation and records smoke artifacts; it cannot honestly claim a tray screenshot on this Crabbox image because the desktop capture handle is invalid.\n",
